{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/extras/QuetzalcoatlInferno500X.gif?t=1738281021\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>&quot;What would you do if the world was ending? Spend time with loved ones? Go on that trip you've always wanted? Or risk everything and try to stop it?&quot;</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sun's Edge is a Hack and Slash Adventure set in a unique Mesoamerican-inspired environment by Indie Developer KC Studios. Explore a vast exotic world, fight strange monsters, and stop Tezcatlipoca before he drowns the world in shadow!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Monsters and Critters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Crystal Skull has corrupted weak minded creatures and monsters. Fight against packs of cursed Crimson monsters that now prowl Cipactlan in their search of Crystal Shards! As you discover new enemies and other exotic critters, you update your Bestiary journal. Can you find them all? Everyone is counting on you to document your findings, and find a way to end the Crimson Curse! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/extras/MacheteCollectSkullPiece500X.gif?t=1738281021\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ITEM'S AND POWER-UPS!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix and match multitudes of items together for combined effects! Try out different weapon types for totally unique playstyles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/extras/Combat1500X.gif?t=1738281021\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mesoamerican Characters and Locations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with interesting characters, explorers and villagers, and complete side quests to earn Ranger Emblems and uncover the game's deeper story! Expand your map as you explore jungles, swamps, waterfalls, deserts, ruins, <span class=\"bb_strike\"><i>the underworld</i></span> and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/extras/Capybara500X.gif?t=1738281021\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Treasure and Collectibles!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you the curious type? Snoop around and find hidden secrets, solve puzzles, and fight bosses to collect gold, weapons, armor, collectibles, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/extras/XochiquetzalBlessing500X.gif?t=1738281021\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2174210?t=1738281021","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738281021","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/46aad1a26fcfe4492750dc93a37159c45da73bf3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738281021","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/46aad1a26fcfe4492750dc93a37159c45da73bf3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738281021","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3123900,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174210/extras/QuetzalcoatlInferno500X.gif?t=1738281021\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>&quot;What would you do if the world was ending? Spend time with loved ones? Go on that trip you've always wanted? Or risk everything and try to stop it?&quot;</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sun's Edge is a Hack and Slash Adventure set in a unique Mesoamerican-inspired e